a take for lowercase chars
A take for uppercase chars

1 variable(v):  first char is lowercase, 1st char of word(except for the 1st word)  in the variable is uppercase.
2. member variable: _v or mV
3. tmp variable:   tV
4. arg         :   aV
5. class name (C):  1st char is uppercase      for example : class  HtmlNode{...};
6. pointer class name(pC):  for example : typedef HtmlNode* pHtmlNode;
7. macro name : all uppercase with "_"
 
